All right guys thanks for listening and be sure to check out our website EnglishPod.com
好了，感谢收听，记得访问我们的网站 EnglishPod.com

247
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:04,620
where you can leave all your questions and comments.
在那里你可以留下所有问题和评论。

248
